KLM Royal Dutch Airlines &lt;KLM.AS>said it is negotiating for a minority stake in a British andCommonwealth Shipping Plc &lt;BCOM.L> courier service in atransaction which might include a convertible loan issue.    KLM, already active in the fast growing door-to-doordelivery market through a 50-pct stake in a Dutch courierservice, is seeking to buy one-third of &lt;IML Air Services GroupLtd> from British and Commonwealth.    The two companies agreed earlier this month for KLM to takea 15-pct stake in British and Commonwealth commuter airline AirU.K. Ltd in a deal worth around two mln stg. Reuter&#3;